<div class = "otherpages">
<h3 class="formc">Hey!<br>In order to get started,we'll use this form as a great starting point for us to understand what you require.Getting to know a few things that have caught your eye and inspired you is also a huge plus.This is just a first step toward brainstorming  your project thoroughly.</h2>
</div>
<div class = "row">
	<div class = "span6 offset5">
		<%= form_for (@customer)  do |f| %>
		  <%= render 'shared/error_messages'%>
		
		   <%= f.label :name %>
		   <%= f.text_field :name,placeholder: "this is obvious :)" %>
		   
		   <%= f.label :email %>
		   <%= f.text_field :email ,placeholder: "the one you regularly check will be perfect here"%>
		   
		   <%= f.label :phone%>
		   <%= f.text_field :phone_number,placeholder: "one you will most likely pick will be good"%>
		   
		   <%= f.label :Your_company_name%>
		   <%= f.text_area :organization, placeholder: "your company or business name",rows: 2 %>
		   
		   <%= f.label :Do_you_have_an_existing_url %>
		   <%= f.text_area :existing_url,placeholder: "e.g yourwebsitename.com,so we can see what you are working with or just ignore this if you dont have one " ,rows: 2%>
		   
		   <%= f.label :describe_your_project%>
		   <%= f.text_area :project_description,placeholder: "a short description will be nice,..we will do it all," ,rows: 3%>
		   
		   <%= f.label :Which_website_inspired_you? %>
		   <%= f.text_area :inspiration,placeholder: "just paste the links here",rows: 4%>
		   
		   <%= f.label :How_soon_do_you_need_it?%>
		   <%= f.text_area :deadline,placeholder: "two weeks? a month?,two months? yesterday is impossible",rows: 4%>
		   
		   
		   <%= f.submit "send your request",class: "btn btn-large btn-primary"%>
		<%end%>
	</div>
</div>

